{"tid":980103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前女團偶像下海拍AV　網友猜真身是這位","createTime":"2019-01-13T09:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T09:03:14.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ff59c77635d7793690a9b7f64ccbf22f0a2d59","tid":980103,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"又有日本前女偶像下海拍AV了！<br />\n<br />\n日本AV商「赤面女子」，將於2月推出前外神田偶像女團10期生木南穗香(木南ほのか)所主演的A片，這樣的宣傳標語，也讓網友肉搜比對，猜測木南穗香可能就是「Bakusute外神田一丁目」的七瀨菜七。而AV女優櫻萌子，也是「Bakusute外神田一丁目」一期生的前成員，之後才加入MUTEKI出道，可算是木南穗香的大前輩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vH8szBL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvH8szBL.png&h=c7d89b89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd608fd062e699a23d5ed03de3cf02820184817","tid":980103,"uid":207005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"波?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}